opentenbase (5.0-1ubuntu1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Multi-version management support.
  * Versioned install prefix: /usr/lib/opentenbase/5.0/
  * Versioned config: /etc/opentenbase/5.0/
  * Versioned data dirs: /var/lib/opentenbase/5.0/
  * Symlink-based version switching via /etc/opentenbase/current
  * New opentenbase-switch-version command for version management
  * Side-by-side installation support for v5.0/v6.0/dev
  * Initial Debian/Ubuntu packaging of OpenTenBase v5.0.
  * 6-package split: opentenbase (metapackage), opentenbase-server,
    opentenbase-client, opentenbase-contrib, libopentenbase-dev,
    opentenbase-doc.
  * systemd unit + opentenbase-ctl smart control script.

 -- OpenTenBase Packaging <packaging@opentenbase.org>  Fri, 23 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000
